{"inkVersion":21,"root":[["^LONDON, 1872","\n","^Residence of Monsieur Phileas Fogg.","\n",{"->":"downtown"},["done",{"#n":"g-0"}],null],"done",{"downtown":["#","^downtown tag","/#","^It was cool downtown. ","#","^tag ya","/#","\n",{"->":"suburbs"},null],"suburbs":["#","^suburbs tag","/#","^Suburbs were cool too. ","#","^tag too","/#","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"health"},2,"-",{"VAR=":"health","re":true},"/ev",{"->":"london"},null],"london":[["#","^health +1","/#","^Monsieur Phileas Fogg returned home early from the Reform Club, and in a new-fangled steam-carriage, besides! ","#","^tag1 ","/#","#","^tag2","/#","\n","^health: \"","ev",{"VAR?":"health"},"out","/ev","^\"","\n","#","^tag 4","/#","^\"Passepartout,\" said he. \"We are going around the world!\" ","#","^tag 3","/#","\n",["ev",{"^->":"london.0.26.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^❤",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"london.0.27.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":18},{"s":["^🙂 ",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"london.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.26.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^I was utterly astonished.","\n",{"->":"astonished"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"london.0.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.27.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],{"->":"nod"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],null],"astonished":[["^\"You are in jest!\" I told him in dignified affront. \"You make mock of me, Monsieur.\"","\n","^\"I am quite serious.\"","\n",["ev",{"^->":"astonished.0.4.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^🙁",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"astonished.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.4.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":"ending"},{"#f":5}]}],null],"nod":["^I nodded curtly, not believing a word of it.","\n",{"->":"ending"},null],"ending":["^\"We shall circumnavigate the globe within eighty days.\"